          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corelocationui"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " framework contains a standardized UI that interacts securely with "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corelocation"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to request authorization to access location data."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corelocationui"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " provides "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corelocationui/locationbutton"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " ("
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corelocationui/cllocationbutton"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " in UIKit), which is a button you add to your UI that allows users to grant your app one-time authorization to fetch their location. The button's style is consistent with the standard "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corelocation"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " design language, giving users a sense of familiarity and trust when they interact with it."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
